Flashing Reaches out to the matrix hoping to call up something I thinking I 
need to gather energy for the Matrix Blaster. As 2 blue shadows seem to hang 
behind Flashing "Cybertorn's Finest." As the first shadow merges with 
Flashing "Optimus Hammer." As a Flash of Optimus seem to appear and doing the 
hammer he used to defeat megatron. 

Dark get nailed Flying back "What in the nine hells" As he stands.

Flashing Rush Forward as 2 blue Shadow merges with him a flash of Rodimus 
Prime appears "Hots Rods Flare." As Flashing  tries to grab Dark.

Dark getting grabbed he tries to struggle but it is seems useless as he tries 
Punches at Flashing.

Flashing chest plates cracks more where dark hits it leaking a massive 
amounts of energy As Flashing throws Dark a Flash appears of Hod Rod throwing 
Galvatron out of Unicron Flashing throwing Dark the same way his Father did. 

Dark Flies through the air skidding on the ground.

Flashing turns back into Liono "It over Dark Convoy you can't beat me."

Dark looks a Liono as he staggers to his feet  "What makes you so special 
that you can't lose to me?" As his anger rises.
